prompts.frontCover: A vibrant comic book panel splash page featuring a dynamic, pop art style illustration of a superhero, "Super Jordan," comically struggling to hold up a giant, multi-layered birthday cake that's tilting precariously. "Super Jordan" is a charming cartoon figure with an exaggerated look of effort on his face, sweat beads flying off his brow. The cake is decorated with explosive "POW!" and "ZAP!" starbursts instead of candles. In the background, use bold Ben-Day dots and speed lines to create a sense of action and energy. A large, stylized speech bubble emerges from near the cake. Inside the bubble, written in beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my Super-Girlfriend, Lao Lao!" The entire scene is framed with a bold black border, typical of a comic book panel, with vibrant, saturated colors like bright reds, yellows, and blues dominating the palette.
